text: :For another species called the Guianan dwarf tree frog, see Lesser tree frog The Guianan dwarf tree frog (Dendropsophus goughi) is a frog that lives in Trinidad. Scientists have seen it as high as 1200 meters above sea level. Scientists used to think this was the same frog as Dendropsophus microcephalus. ==References== Category:Frogs of South America
title: Dendropsophus goughi
